  <Comments>* Games with timers:
=&gt; see 'Timers' section
 
* Poker Game:
=&gt; see 'Poker Hand Money': just reduce them player's clip money to '5' (or less);
   this will usually get all of them busted after a few rounds...
 
* Drinking Game:
=&gt; use 'Set Speed' to slow down the game's speed, making it really easy to finish it...
   (uses CE's standard 'Speedhack' feature)
 
* Shell Game:
=&gt; main cheat: increase your 'Calibration' (via Options) to 'see' the ball really easy,
   upon pausing (press [ESC])
=&gt; without cheating:
1. 1st round should be easy; ball remains under the same cup
2. 2nd/3rd round: he will lift the "initial" cup at some point, basically moving the ball
   to another cup !
   The "lifting" is always done to the left side (from the player's point of view);
   iow you'll need to follow the cup on that side thereafter...
3. beyond the 3rd round, you'll actually see the ball "switching"...
Note: you could also use 'Set Speed' here
</Comments>
  <LuaScript>-- You must accept to execute
-- the script !
-- If not, the CE table
-- will return errors...


